    "created_at": "2016-05-30T02:07:06Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-30T02:07:27Z",
    "body": "The `transparent` option is required to be used together with `frame: false`, and the behavior is undefined if you use `transparent: true` in a window with frame. This rule is not enforced in code, but if you don't follow it you are on your own when you met any bug.\n\nFor this bug, I'm cool fixing it if it doesn't take much efforts.\n\n@xMrWhite That commit is part of #5557 which fixes another bug.\n"
  },
