    "created_at": "2016-05-30T02:32:49Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-30T02:32:49Z",
    "body": "@zcbenz Something changed so that [this code block](https://github.com/electron/electron/blob/master/atom/browser/native_window_mac.mm#L516) is not behaving correctly.\n\nA better example is\n\n```\nmainWindow = new BrowserWindow({\n  width: 800,\n  height: 600,\n  titleBarStyle: 'hidden',\n  minimizable: false,\n  maximizable: false\n});\n```\n\nWhich creates this:\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/3745612/15638323/07576618-25ed-11e6-9a81-db90b55bbee8.png)\n\nCalling `setMaximizable(false)` afterwards will disable the button so the function itself is fine.\n"
  },
