    "created_at": "2016-06-01T13:23:04Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-06-01T13:23:40Z",
    "body": "For anyone looking for a quick hacky fix until this is resolved then @danhp's suggestion of doing `setMaximizable(false)` works well.\n\n``` js\nconst win = new BrowserWindow({\n  // ...\n  maximizable: false\n});\n\nwin.setMaximizable(false); // HACK: remove when #5745 is resolved.\n```\n"
